item.description: Franc is working on a bachelor thesis aimed at elucidating the role of hormone secretion and hormone receptors with a focus on secretin in the human gut. He is jointly supervised by Michael Lauber and Andrea Bast-Habersbrunner from the group of Prof. Martin Klingenspor.
